        <type name="CM_XlationInByForeignCodeDict"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>Inward translations keyed on foreign code.  Could be more
the one translation per foreign code,e.g voyages may hve same voyage number
across different vessels.

*** need key of foreign default ***

If matching on just 1st 20 characters of foreign code then we will use
foreignDefault if there is &gt; 1 match.</text>
        <Inverse name="CM_Xlation::myXlationTable"/>
